	"VersionName": "0.17.0",
	"FriendlyName": "Monolith",
	"Description": "Unified Unreal Engine MCP server — 1348 actions across 19 in-tree namespaces (Blueprint 111, Material 63, Animation 125, Niagara 109, Mesh 194, Editor 33, Config 6, Source 11, Project 7, UI 138, GAS 135, ComboGraph 13, AI 221, LogicDriver 66, Audio 98, LevelSequence 8, monolith meta 5, bulk_fill 2, describe 3). +45 experimental town-gen actions register when `bEnableProceduralTownGen=true`. Framework-level `bulk_fill_query` and `describe_query` route to 12 per-namespace adapters for transacted JSON-tree writes and rich schema introspection. AI-powered asset creation, inspection, and modification.",
	"Category": "Editor",
	"CreatedBy": "tumourlove",
